  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exclusive Spacecraft",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属飞船",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊太空船"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>, pre-fitted with a powerful <span class=\"name name-technology\">Phase Beam</span> and upgraded <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Engine</span> for efficient space exploration. The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Economy Scanner</span> also allows for remote access to detailed economic data about a system, assisting in planning galactic trade routes.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，预装有能够高效探索太空的强大<span class=\"name name-technology\">相位光束</span>和升级版<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲驱动器</span>。<span class=\"name name-technology\">经济扫描仪</span>可远程访问星系的详细经济数据，协助规划星际贸易路线。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，預裝了強大的<span class=\"name name-technology\">相位光束</span>與升級的<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝引擎</span>，能夠有效率探索銀河。此外，<span class=\"name name-technology\">經濟掃描器</span>也能從遠端獲得星系的詳細經濟資料，有助於規劃銀河貿易路線。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可以從快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
